General.Name: Jiankun International Bhd
General.Description: Jiankun International Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in property development and construction business in Malaysia and the People's Republic of China. The company operates through two segments, Property Development and Construction, and Property Management and Investment Holding. It develops and provides construction services for residential, industrial, and commercial properties. The company also offers project management, marketing, and consultancy services. In addition, it engages in general trading and general contractor for buildings. The company was formerly known as Nagamas International Berhad and changed its name to Jiankun International Berhad in March 2014. The company is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.
